"     Original figure modified for this publication. Martinez AE. Tests to monitor in patients with severe types of epidermolysis bullosa. Dermatol Clin 2010; 28:271. Table used with the permission of Elsevier Inc. All rights reserved.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
